text: Deonne Ellen Bridger is an archer from Australia. Bridger competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics.Deonne BRIDGER She was born on 15 May 1972.Deonne Bridger == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Australian archers Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Sportspeople from Perth, Western Australia
